      • GameSquare

        public GameSquare(int x,
                  int y,
                  java.lang.String filename,
                  GameBoard board)
        Create a new GameSquare, which can be placed on a GameBoard.
        参数:
        x - the x co-ordinate of this square on the game board.
        y - the y co-ordinate of this square on the game board.
        board - the GameBoard upon which this square resides.
        filename - file name.
